ght\nsneutrinos, charginos or neutralinos. Besides, $Z'$ and Higgs mediated\nannihilations and interactions with the visible sector of WIMP dark matter\nparticles, can also be present.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2021 12:24:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 May 2021 17:16:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
