his result but, as of now, we conclude that the CDDR favours a flat Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2021 12:57:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 15:48:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
